cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.MM 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image segmentation using a novel network architecture. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a new method for incorporating edge prior knowledge in the segmentation process. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper involves end-to-end training of the proposed network architecture. 
4. cs.RO (Robotics) is a potential category as thermal imaging is commonly used in robotics for object detection and tracking. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with image segmentation in thermal images, which is a type of multimedia data.
